Enum Permission

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Permission>
      • eu.casoftworks.jdroidlib.enums.Permission
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Permission>

    public enum Permission
extends java.lang.Enum<Permission>
    Defines different permissions found on a Linux file system.
